name: Rogue 4K
overview: You are Zendar Slickweed. You have wandered the earth for what felt like eons, looking for interesting dungeons to explore. At last you have found what you are seeking! The dungeons of Rogonia are waiting! You are hunting for gold and fame. Mostly fame, but the gold is nice to have too! The only problem is that there are evil cave dwellers lurking in the dark waiting to kill you as you travel deeper and deeper into this cube-like terror maze. Aim of the game: get as far and deep as you can ! Get the highest score. Will yu get to the infamous killscreen? Published in The C64 'Cassette 50' Charity Cassette.
